headline: Billionaire Israel Englander Bought This High-Yield Dividend Stock Hand Over Fist in Q3. Should You Buy It Too?
summary: Israel "Izzy" Englander's net worth tops $14 billion.  The billionaire bought one high-yield dividend stock hand over fist in Q3.  If you glance at Englander's purchases for Millennium Management in Q3, you'll probably notice he added significantly to several existing holdings.
